Plugin Step: Configure Cloud Provider CLI
Usage: 
CLI Base, The base directory for CLI.
Host Name specifies the host name of the cloud provider.
Type specifies the type of the cloud provider, which could be either iwd or ipas.

This step will copy the command line tool to CLI base directory. 